            x1       x2       x3       x4
   y1  -0.9844    0.178   -13.84   -2.492
   y2   -0.178   -0.984   -2.492   -14.74
 
d = 
       u1
   y1   0
   y2   0
 
Continuous-time model.

% controller transfer-function
zpk(ctr1)
 
